{
  "stem": "428.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, the glasses, that's right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I took them so you wouldn't sit on them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I work on a lathe and a tool fell down from the lathe, any tool, I couldn't bend down and pick up the tool.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was so weak already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they had automatic-- automatic cranes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I pushed the button, the crane came, and he picked it up for me because I couldn't pick it up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was working there-- I was working there till in May.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, it was-- this was the worst camp from all, the hunger.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the only thing you did for food was scraping this paint?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they give you--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They give you, have a quart of water, potato peels-- potato peels and water, yeah, potato peels and water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I forgot to tell you, while I was working where I was-- oh, St.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Valentin.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before I came to-- to-- yeah, before I came to Mauthausen, I used to work in a-- in a-- in a factory there too on a lathe.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had a foreman, an Austrian man, Leo Humpel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had a little closet by my lathe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I came in the morning, I opened that closet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was boil-- broil a little bit, baked potatoes, he used to bring me, that German, Leo Humpel from-- from-- I know the others.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Steiner, was a very nice man, an Austrian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then when-- that camp, the last one, was Ebensee, was the worstest camp in the world.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The hunger.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The hunger is terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is-- is-- you have no idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody should know about this, what hunger is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're going around, your mind is only in one direction, where to get something to eat, where to get something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't care nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
